operations.body: mutation NestedUpload($topFile: Upload, $topFileList: [Upload], $nested: NestedObject) { nestedUpload(topFile: $topFile, topFileList: $topFileList, nested: $nested) }
operations.name: NestedUpload

operations.body: mutation SingleUploadTwice($file1: Upload!, $file2: Upload!) { file1: singleUpload(file: $file1) { id path filename mimetype } file2: singleUpload(file: $file2) { id path filename mimetype } }
operations.name: SingleUploadTwice

operations.body: mutation MultipleUpload($files: [Upload!]!) { multipleUpload(files: $files) { id path filename mimetype } }
operations.name: MultipleUpload

operations.body: mutation SingleUpload($file: Upload!) { singleUpload(file: $file) { id path filename mimetype } }
operations.name: SingleUpload
